@lillolollo, It is indeed still present on 2.10.10

@mitch, The problem as I see it, is that the "Search and Run a Command" should be treated as a dialog,but it is presented to the window manager as a normal window (`_NET_WM_WINDOW_TYPE_NORMAL`).

In comparison, the About window presented as a dialog (`_NET_WM_WINDOW_TYPE_DIALOG`) and is therefore handled as such (a floating window)

